<ptxt>
OCV and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P2088: “A” Camshaft Position Actuator Control Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OCV control circuit is shorted to ground.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P2089: “A” Camshaft Position Actuator Control Circuit High
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OCV control circuit is shorted to power supply.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
